vpk-html
========

vpk-html is part of the VPK-Rovo monorepo and inherits its licensing terms.
The VPK-Rovo monorepo is currently private; see the repository root for
authoritative licensing.

Third-party material
====================

The 14 SVG diagram primitives in `assets/diagrams/` are ported from
tw93/kami (https://github.com/tw93/Kami) and re-skinned with vpk-html's
visual identity. The SVG geometry is kami's work, used under the MIT License.

  kami — Copyright (c) tw93
  MIT License — https://github.com/tw93/Kami/blob/main/LICENSE

The fonts shipped under `assets/fonts/` are committed local font assets used
to preserve the offline HTML artifact contract:

  - Charlie Display
  - Charlie Text
  - Atlassian Mono

Attribution is preserved in README.md.
